Name: Oncolytics Biotech Inc
Description: Oncolytics Biotech Inc., a development stage biopharmaceutical company, focuses on the discovery and development of pharmaceutical products for the treatment of cancer. Its lead product is pelareorep, an immuno-oncology viral-agent for the treatment of solid tumors and hematological malignancies. The company has collaboration agreements with Merck KGaA and Pfizer Inc. to co-develop pelareorep in combination with paclitaxel and avelumab, a human anti-PD-L1 antibody for the treatment of hormone-receptor positive, human epidermal growth factor 2-negative metastatic breast cancer; and PrECOG LLC. Oncolytics Biotech Inc. was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
Address: 1167 Kensington Crescent NW, Calgary, AB, Canada, T2N 1X7
